and the third load would
never get to town.

30:45.411 --> 30:46.810
- It doesn't do me any good

30:46.812 --> 30:48.178
standing here looking at it

30:48.180 --> 30:49.713
when I gotta get
to the other side.

30:49.715 --> 30:52.449
The longer I stand here
the wetter it's gonna get.

30:54.286 --> 30:57.054
I guess I'll take the route
less traveled.

30:58.657 --> 31:00.123
(door shuts)

31:01.493 --> 31:02.893
(engine roars)

31:02.895 --> 31:13.003
♪ ♪

31:13.005 --> 31:16.006
a lot of water coming
through here right now.

31:16.008 --> 31:18.609
This ain't gonna last long,
I'm telling ya.

31:18.611 --> 31:22.446
♪ ♪

31:22.448 --> 31:25.682
quite a spot to get stuck
if things don't change.

31:25.684 --> 31:27.117
(splashing)

31:28.487 --> 31:30.087
holy (bleep).

31:30.089 --> 31:36.860
♪ ♪

31:36.862 --> 31:38.528
here we go.

31:41.200 --> 31:42.833
Narrator: With the creek
behind him

31:42.835 --> 31:46.370
